_sText:
In September 2014, I was calling out the idea to run a community mapping project. Everyone had the same sized piece of land in hammer editor and was free to create whatever he/she wanted. A bit sadly only 3 mappers made it in time but the idea and project is what counts. Recently I was able to finish the project and this is the result. :)

You can watch the ingame video here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DvRsYTiXtGQ
